Insider Activity


Individual




Kelly W. Hoffman



Mr. Kelly W. Hoffman is Chief Executive Officer & Director at Ring Energy, Inc. and Independent Director at Differential Brands Group, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Ring Energy, Inc. and Differential Brands Group, Inc.
Mr. Hoffman was previously employed as President by Victory Park Resources LLC, Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Varsity Media Group, Inc., Owner by Aoco Operating Co. LLC, and President & Chief Executive Officer by Victory Park Resources Corp. He also served on the board at Joe's Jeans, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Texas Tech University.



