About UsHoffman Kelly is a Chartered Accounting firm with the head office situated in Coorparoo, Brisbane.  The firm has four directors and an overall team of over forty.
Our team is dedicated to supporting clients and assisting them reach their full potential through innovative and cutting edge structuring and ongoing proactive advice.
We pride ourselves on providing an outstanding service and exceeding clients expectations and, due almost exclusively to client referrals,  we have grown sigifianctly over the last five years to become one of the largest Chartered Accounting firms outside the CBD.
We foster two core objectives:-

Recruit and retain the brightest and best, and

Ensure we are at the absolute cutting edge in terms of business structuring and tax effective solutions

We believe any success has come by understanding that these objectives are completely interrelated.
We spend a huge amount of time and resources (substantially more than our peers) on professional development for all professional staff.
In turn we have successfully retained the brightest graduates and have developed a young dynamic team at the absolute cutting edge of business structuring and emerging opportunities.





 
 
 





